{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2018/10/05/akka-testing-helpers-v2/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Akka Testing Helpers V2","description":"Announcing Akka Testing Helpers V2","date":"2018-10-05T17:00:00.000Z","showReadingTime":null,"toc":null,"presentation":null,"languages":["C#"],"technologies":["Akka.NET"]},"excerpt":"Introduction For an introduction into what the Akka Testing Helpers project is, please see the solution's new readme on GitHub. Upgrading To V2 I have removed …","html":"<h1 id=\"introduction\" style=\"position:relative;\">Introduction<a href=\"#introduction\" aria-label=\"introduction permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p>For an introduction into what the Akka Testing Helpers project is, please see the solution's new <a href=\"https://github.com/connelhooley/AkkaTestingHelpers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">readme on GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h1 id=\"upgrading-to-v2\" style=\"position:relative;\">Upgrading To V2<a href=\"#upgrading-to-v2\" aria-label=\"upgrading to v2 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p>I have removed the versions of this package from NuGet that were versioned by date (for example <code>2018.3.6.2</code>) and uploaded a new package with the version <code>2.0.0</code>. This is to honour semantic versioning going forward.</p>\n<h1 id=\"breaking-changes\" style=\"position:relative;\">Breaking Changes<a href=\"#breaking-changes\" aria-label=\"breaking changes permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p>There are 2 tiny breaking changes between version <code>2018.3.6.2</code> and version <code>2.0.0</code>. A quick find and replace should be all that is needed. Now proper versioning is in place upgrades should be smoother in the future.</p>\n<h2 id=\"registerhandler\" style=\"position:relative;\">RegisterHandler<a href=\"#registerhandler\" aria-label=\"registerhandler permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>The <code>RegisterHandler</code> method on the settings class is now called <code>RegisterChildHandler</code>.</p>\n\n        <div class=\"code-copy-wrapper\">\n          <button class=\"code-copy-button\" onClick=\"_codeToClipboard(event);\">Copy</button>\n          <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Old:</span>\nUnitTestFrameworkSettings<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Empty<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token generic-method\"><span class=\"token function\">RegisterHandler</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ExampleActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> i <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// New:</span>\nUnitTestFrameworkSettings<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Empty<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token generic-method\"><span class=\"token function\">RegisterChildHandler</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ExampleActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> i <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n        </div>\n<h2 id=\"supervisor\" style=\"position:relative;\">Supervisor<a href=\"#supervisor\" aria-label=\"supervisor permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>The <code>Supervisor</code> property has been renamed to <code>Parent</code>.</p>\n\n        <div class=\"code-copy-wrapper\">\n          <button class=\"code-copy-button\" onClick=\"_codeToClipboard(event);\">Copy</button>\n          <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Old:</span>\nframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Supervisor<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Expect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// New:</span>\nframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Parent<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Expect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hello world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n        </div>\n<h1 id=\"new-features\" style=\"position:relative;\">New Features<a href=\"#new-features\" aria-label=\"new features permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p>There are 3 new features in version 2.0.0.</p>\n<h2 id=\"parent-handlers\" style=\"position:relative;\">Parent Handlers<a href=\"#parent-handlers\" aria-label=\"parent handlers permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>You can now add handlers to the parent test probe:</p>\n\n        <div class=\"code-copy-wrapper\">\n          <button class=\"code-copy-button\" onClick=\"_codeToClipboard(event);\">Copy</button>\n          <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token class-name\">UnitTestFramework<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>SutActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> framework <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> UnitTestFrameworkSettings\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Empty\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token generic-method\"><span class=\"token function\">RegisterParentHandler</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Save<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token constructor-invocation class-name\">ModifiedSave</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Value<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ToUpper</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token generic-method\"><span class=\"token function\">CreateFramework</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>SutActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n        </div>\n<p>The example above creates an instance of <code>SutActor</code> with a parent TestProbe that receives <code>Save</code> messages and replies with <code>ModifiedSave</code> messages.</p>\n<h2 id=\"unhandled-exceptions\" style=\"position:relative;\">Unhandled Exceptions<a href=\"#unhandled-exceptions\" aria-label=\"unhandled exceptions permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>You can now send a message into the SUT actor and wait for an exception to be thrown. There is also a new property on the UnitTestFramework that allows you to access unhandled exceptions.</p>\n\n        <div class=\"code-copy-wrapper\">\n          <button class=\"code-copy-button\" onClick=\"_codeToClipboard(event);\">Copy</button>\n          <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token comment\">//arrange</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">Exception</span> message <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token constructor-invocation class-name\">ArithmeticException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">UnitTestFramework<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>SutActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> framework <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> UnitTestFrameworkSettings\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Empty\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token generic-method\"><span class=\"token function\">CreateFramework</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>SutActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//act</span>\nframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">TellMessageAndWaitForException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>message<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//assert</span>\nframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>UnhandledExceptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">First</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Should</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">BeSameAs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>message<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n        </div>\n<p>The example above creates an instance of <code>SutActor</code>, then sends it a message. In this example the message is an exception and the <code>StuActor</code> throws any exceptions it receives. The <code>TellMessageAndWaitForException</code> method blocks the thread until the exception is thrown. The <code>UnhandledExceptions</code> property is then used to assert the correct exception is thrown.</p>\n<p>This feature keeps inline with the framework's philosophy of removing hard-coded wait times.</p>\n<h2 id=\"delay\" style=\"position:relative;\">Delay<a href=\"#delay\" aria-label=\"delay permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>You can now block the current thread by a certain period of time. The main benefit of this feature is that it works like the rest of the Akka TestKit by multiplying the given duration by the configured timefactor.</p>\n\n        <div class=\"code-copy-wrapper\">\n          <button class=\"code-copy-button\" onClick=\"_codeToClipboard(event);\">Copy</button>\n          <div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csharp\"><pre class=\"language-csharp\"><code class=\"language-csharp\"><span class=\"token class-name\">UnitTestFramework<span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>SutActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> framework <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> UnitTestFrameworkSettings\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Empty\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token generic-method\"><span class=\"token function\">CreateFramework</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>SutActor<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Sync</span>\nframework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Delay</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TimeSpan<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">FromSeconds</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Async</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> framework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">DelayAsync</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TimeSpan<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">FromSeconds</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n        </div>\n<p>The above example blocks the thread by 3 seconds if the given TestKit instance has a <code>timefactor</code> of 3. Using this method allows you to modify all of your currently hard-coded delays by the <code>timefactor</code>.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#introduction\">Introduction</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#upgrading-to-v2\">Upgrading To V2</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#breaking-changes\">Breaking Changes</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#registerhandler\">RegisterHandler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#supervisor\">Supervisor</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#new-features\">New Features</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#parent-handlers\">Parent Handlers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#unhandled-exceptions\">Unhandled Exceptions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#delay\">Delay</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":3},"prev":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2020/05/14/react-styling/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Styling React Apps"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2018/04/10/git-presentation/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Git Presentation"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2018/10/05/akka-testing-helpers-v2/","prevSlug":"/blog/2020/05/14/react-styling/","nextSlug":"/blog/2018/04/10/git-presentation/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3096703167"]}